\v 5 We \add Israelis\add* have sinnedВҰ361744 and done wrongВҰ361745. We have \add вүҲdone wicked things\add* and rebelledВҰ361748 \add against you\add*, \add вүҲnot wanting to obey\add* your rules and instructions.
\v 6 We \add вүҲignored the challenges from\add* your servantsВҰ361757 the prophetsВҰ361758 who spokeВҰ361760 to our kingsВҰ361764, our \add вүҲgeneralsВҰ361765\add*, and our ancestorsВҰ361766 \add вүҲonВҰ361761 your behalf\add*, and to all the peopleВҰ361770 of the land.
