\v 11 All YisraelВҰ361837 has \add вүҲbroken\add* your law and turnedВҰ361842 awayвҖ”not obeying your \add вүҲwords\add*. The curseВҰ361848 and oath thatВҰ361850 are writtenВҰ361851 inВҰ361845 the law \add вүҲgiven through\add* \add *your\add* servantВҰ361854 MoshehВҰ361853, have been \add вүҲapplied to\add* us, because weВҰ361858 have sinnedВҰ361858 against \add вүҲyou\add*.
