\v 13 As it's writtenВҰ361892 inВҰ361893 the Mosheh'sВҰ361894 law, \add вүҲwe've undergone\add* all that calamityВҰ361898, yet we haven't \add вүҲtried to earn\add* our god Yahweh'a favour our god by turningВҰ361911 away from our \add вүҲdisobedience\add* and givingВҰ361913 attentionВҰ361913 to yourВҰ361914 truthВҰ361914.
\v 14 Therefore Yahweh keptВҰ361916 \add вүҲpondering the need for\add* calamityВҰ361920 and thenВҰ361916 \add eventually\add* broughtВҰ361921 it onВҰ361937 us, because our godВҰ361927 Yahweh is \add вүҲalways does what is rightВҰ361925\add* and \add yet\add* we haven't obeyed \add вүҲwhat he said\add*.
