\v 17 SoВҰ361986 now, our godВҰ361989, listenВҰ361988 to the prayerВҰ361992 of your servantВҰ361993 andВҰ361986 to his pleas for mercy. ForВҰ361989 your sake, my masterВҰ362004, \add вүҲshow favour to your devastated\add* sanctuaryВҰ362001.
