\v 24 \add вүҲIt's been decreedВҰ362129 that there'll be 490\add* \add years\add* for your peopleВҰ362132 and your holy cityВҰ362136, to stop the transgressionВҰ362139, to put an endВҰ362140 to sinВҰ362142, to \add вүҲpay the price\add* for \add вүҲdisobedience\add*, to bringВҰ362146 in righteousnessВҰ362147 \add вүҲthat will then last forever\add*, to seal up visionВҰ362150 and prophecyВҰ362151, and to anointВҰ362152 the most holy placeВҰ362153. NEEDS MORE WORK
