\p
\v 1 In the third year of \add the reign\add* of Persian KingВҰ362231 Koresh \add (Cyrus)\add*, a message was revealedВҰ362234 to Daniel (also named Belteshatstsar). The message was true, and it \add concerned\add* was a large conflictВҰ362243. He understood the message and had an understanding of the visionВҰ362251.
