\v 2 \add вүҲAt that time\add*, I, Daniel, had been mourningВҰ362258 for threeВҰ362259 weeks.
\v 3 I hadn't eaten any tasty food or meat, \add вүҲand no wine had been near my lips\add*. I hadn't even \add вүҲput any perfumed oil on\add* my hair or face during those threeВҰ362282 weeks.
